Privacy Policy for Squares
Introduction
Welcome to Squares! This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our mobile game app. By downloading and playing Squares, you agree to the terms described below.

Information We Collect
Game Data: We collect gameplay data, such as your high scores, achievements, and progress within the game.
Device Information: We may collect information about your device, including its model, operating system, and unique device identifiers.
Analytics: We use third-party analytics tools (e.g., Google Analytics) to understand user behavior and improve our app. These tools may collect anonymous data about your interactions with Squares.
How We Use Your Information
Game Improvement: We analyze gameplay data to enhance the gaming experience, fix bugs, and optimize performance.
Personalization: We may use analytics to tailor in-game content based on your preferences.
Legal Compliance: We comply with legal requirements, including privacy laws and regulations.
Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, loss, or misuse. However, please note that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure.

Third-Party Services
Squares integrates with third-party services (e.g., ad networks, analytics providers). Please review their privacy policies to understand how they handle your data.

